WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.796
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.820 --> 01:30.708
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 19=

01:30.708 --> 01:35.203
(Whatever part of me you like,
it's still me, right?)

01:50.220 --> 01:56.440
I smell good after having the food
made from osmanthus.

02:00.180 --> 02:01.280
Are you sleepy?

02:03.539 --> 02:08.919
- Yeah. But I can keep going.
- You should just get some sleep if so.

02:12.180 --> 02:14.239
Sleeping here overnight?

02:16.459 --> 02:21.359
It's not a whole night.
Daylight is less than two hours away.

02:41.060 --> 02:46.000
I was asking you to put down the cup.
You should fetch a new one for yourself.

02:48.900 --> 02:51.079
I don't mind you used it.

02:56.979 --> 03:03.880
My grandpa never drinks from a used cup.
I thought you were the same.

03:06.060 --> 03:07.440
To others, yes.

03:18.019 --> 03:19.959
I'll tell you a secret.

03:22.259 --> 03:27.619
- Remember the slogan on your forum?
- Yes.

03:27.619 --> 03:34.120
Everyone has emotions. It's better
not to meet a beauty in the beginning.

03:38.019 --> 03:43.359
I've used this phrase
as my signature line

03:47.060 --> 03:50.519
since the start of falling

03:56.220 --> 03:57.560
for your voice

03:58.699 --> 04:00.280
for two years.

04:03.539 --> 04:09.159
Later, as your fame grew, I changed it,
as I thought it might not be proper.

04:16.259 --> 04:18.120
You can change back now.

04:20.420 --> 04:24.480
Now, the phrase is appropriate.

04:29.820 --> 04:33.920
What if after I change it back,

04:34.779 --> 04:36.360
we break up?

04:36.980 --> 04:38.839
That would be even more embarrassing.

04:41.339 --> 04:44.320
You are always prepared for the worst?

04:48.380 --> 04:51.399
Why? Where did I fall short?

04:58.860 --> 05:01.079
It's just that you did too well.

05:03.579 --> 05:05.199
Worrying about gains and losses.

05:14.752 --> 05:19.444
♪ Which sound soaks the green plums ♪

05:20.856 --> 05:25.364
♪ Which sound wrinkles the blue sky ♪

05:26.648 --> 05:30.848
♪ Shedding an invisible spring rain ♪

05:30.848 --> 05:37.396
♪ The world is drunk at a timid moment ♪

05:38.712 --> 05:43.476
♪ We talk and laugh
as if we are holding hands ♪

05:44.600 --> 05:50.880
♪ We stay silent
like falling behind the sunset ♪

05:50.880 --> 05:54.780
♪ That moment is still lingering ♪

05:55.019 --> 05:56.320
Aren't you tired?

05:59.940 --> 06:01.000
Take a nap?

06:03.391 --> 06:10.093
♪ There seems to be a river
flowing through my heart ♪

06:13.459 --> 06:17.599
Don't forget we have a morning flight.

06:19.180 --> 06:20.440
Got it.

06:22.047 --> 06:28.083
♪ Each sound is a promise of forever
to a lifetime ♪

06:31.180 --> 06:33.680
- Good night.
- Good night.

06:33.823 --> 06:38.977
♪ Whenever I hear you,
my heart flutters a thousand times ♪

06:38.977 --> 06:42.631
♪ Birds fly past spring and autumn
once again ♪

06:42.631 --> 06:46.139
♪ The splendid world still remains ♪

06:46.623 --> 06:50.023
♪ Gifting us freedom ♪

06:50.023 --> 06:54.924
♪ We ferment each other into wine ♪

06:56.031 --> 07:02.172
♪ Within the intoxication, I can feel ♪

07:02.540 --> 07:04.920
Hey. Hello.

07:05.940 --> 07:07.959
You are a celebrity?

07:09.940 --> 07:10.959
No, I'm not.

07:14.139 --> 07:16.360
I'm only a celebrity
in my girlfriend's heart.

07:19.139 --> 07:20.320
She's drunk.

08:05.699 --> 08:07.279
Good morning.

08:12.019 --> 08:13.120
Morning.

08:15.699 --> 08:16.800
It's dawn.

08:21.339 --> 08:23.079
It's so beautiful.

08:31.459 --> 08:33.199
The tea in the morning is different?

08:37.099 --> 08:42.079
He specifically asked
what we drink here in the morning.

08:42.079 --> 08:47.140
And I told him it was oil tea.
It was his idea to make it.

08:47.140 --> 08:51.640
I guess he wanted you
to experience the authentic flavor.

08:56.459 --> 09:00.879
- Thank you.
- Don't mention it, Shengshengman.

09:09.540 --> 09:10.640
And also this.

09:21.619 --> 09:23.400
Eating sweets just after waking up

09:24.660 --> 09:25.879
will make my day.

09:32.219 --> 09:33.839
What do you think now?

09:35.379 --> 09:36.760
Are we suitable?

09:41.619 --> 09:46.320
- What if we're not suitable?
- What if we're suitable?

09:47.420 --> 09:51.400
You won't know the end
if you don't even start it.

09:54.060 --> 09:56.879
So far,

09:58.020 --> 09:59.239
almost.

09:59.820 --> 10:01.119
Almost?

10:02.260 --> 10:03.640
How much different?

10:05.820 --> 10:09.879
Just pretty good.

10:13.499 --> 10:14.920
Yet it's not the best?

10:20.379 --> 10:24.479
You can be very aggressive at times.

10:25.060 --> 10:26.160
Really?

10:27.619 --> 10:28.999
Like right now.

10:42.260 --> 10:45.420
- Be careful.
- Come again next time.

10:45.420 --> 10:48.680
- Thank you.
- Thanks for your hard work. Let's go.

11:01.780 --> 11:03.199
Didn't they answer?

11:04.219 --> 11:07.059
They've all slept through.
Let's go to the restaurant first.

11:07.059 --> 11:09.839
We can order them
some breakfast to their rooms.

11:10.780 --> 11:15.304
I only knew Doudou and Juemei
were in charge.

11:15.304 --> 11:18.640
Actually, you were taking care of
everyone behind the scenes.

11:50.420 --> 11:54.780
- Time to get up. A plane to catch.
- It's too late. A plane to catch.

11:54.780 --> 11:56.619
- Xiaoxing, Doudou, get up.
- Get up!

11:56.619 --> 11:57.699
- What's going on?
- Get up!

11:57.699 --> 11:59.820
- We've got to catch the plane.
- My phone is gone!

11:59.820 --> 12:02.020
Get up, hurry! Come out now!
We've got to catch the plane.

12:02.020 --> 12:02.780
Sheng.

12:02.780 --> 12:08.100
Hurry up. Everyone, listen to me.
Wash up and have breakfast here.

12:08.100 --> 12:10.980
Then go back to your rooms to pack.

12:10.980 --> 12:13.859
Only about half an hour for wash-up,
breakfast and pack-up.

12:13.859 --> 12:15.060
- Cheer up.
- Here.

12:15.060 --> 12:19.300
Come back! If you don't brush your teeth,
no one will want you. Go.

12:19.300 --> 12:21.699
- Hurry up.
- Wait for me.

12:21.699 --> 12:24.239
- You're not washing up?
- I'll go back and wash up.

12:28.499 --> 12:29.800
I will brush my teeth.

12:33.300 --> 12:36.640
- Am I not brushing properly?
- Hurry up. We're going to be late.

12:37.979 --> 12:39.300
- Steamed dumplings.
- I found my phone.

12:39.300 --> 12:40.640
This is quite delicious.

12:42.699 --> 12:44.440
This is tasty. Try it.

12:45.379 --> 12:47.760
- Let me try.
- Look.

12:49.499 --> 12:50.920
It's good!

12:51.940 --> 12:53.839
They're getting along now.

12:55.099 --> 12:58.760
Friendship at the card table
tends to grow quickly.

13:00.540 --> 13:03.239
Try this one. It's tasty.

13:07.940 --> 13:11.079
- No osmanthus food anymore after this.
- I'm used to it.

13:11.900 --> 13:16.299
- We should share that porridge.
- She must want one for herself.

13:16.299 --> 13:18.960
She's my sister.
I'm close enough with her.

13:18.960 --> 13:23.599
I won't share the porridge with you.
You didn't even brush your teeth well.

13:23.599 --> 13:30.000
- I brushed my teeth and used mouthwash!
- You're so weird to do that.

13:30.000 --> 13:33.360
- Pediatricians cares oral hygiene most.
- You are not a dentist.

13:33.360 --> 13:34.479
Exactly.

13:35.260 --> 13:39.196
When kids are young,
parents all come to me for any illness.

13:39.304 --> 13:43.420
They drink milk and love sweets,
so they get cavities easily.

13:43.496 --> 13:47.100
I keep telling them to care about teeth.
Now I even got into the same habit.

13:47.208 --> 13:52.368
I'll use dental floss first, brush teeth,
and then use mouthwash.

13:52.392 --> 13:55.800
Actually, I simplified it here. Here.

13:57.339 --> 14:00.800
I'm not sharing the porridge with you.
I'll have rice noodles.

14:05.660 --> 14:08.680
- So reluctant to go back.
- We'll come back next time.

14:11.517 --> 14:14.680
(Airport)

14:16.060 --> 14:17.079
We're leaving.

14:17.619 --> 14:20.120
- Don't leave, you two.
- Forget it. I don't want you bothering.

14:20.120 --> 14:22.640
- Right.
- Take care, Zhu.

14:24.219 --> 14:25.400
Come on.

14:27.780 --> 14:29.760
- Thanks for the hospitality.
- Come visit often.

14:33.499 --> 14:35.760
- Here.
- Take care.

14:38.180 --> 14:40.199
- Feel free to come anytime.
- Thank you.

14:44.579 --> 14:47.079
Come on, stop crying.

14:47.619 --> 14:51.640
- A big boss like you crying like that?
- We'll meet again someday.

14:52.219 --> 14:55.479
- What are you doing?
- When I'm with you guys,

14:56.940 --> 14:58.680
I feel like I'm back in my twenties.

15:01.020 --> 15:03.520
I'll come to you
for a five-day luxury tour then.

15:05.260 --> 15:11.679
- Fine. I'm worried that you won't come.
- Go ahead. I'll leave it here.

15:11.679 --> 15:13.180
- Bye.
- Bye.

15:13.180 --> 15:15.240
- Goodbye.
- Go on, goodbye.

15:15.240 --> 15:16.099
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

15:16.099 --> 15:18.000
- Come to see us when you have time.
- Okay.

15:18.000 --> 15:19.640
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

15:20.300 --> 15:22.839
- Goodbye.
- Remember to call me.

15:23.699 --> 15:24.920
Don't forget the gifts.

15:36.379 --> 15:38.640
Boss, you're so emotional.

15:39.900 --> 15:41.680
We met before I got rich.

15:43.579 --> 15:45.479
Even if I get to know other friends,

15:46.180 --> 15:48.160
it won't be as close as to them.

15:53.579 --> 15:54.680
Let's go.

16:04.812 --> 16:09.052
(Girl's Dorm Building 3)

16:20.140 --> 16:21.920
It really feels like a dream.

16:22.780 --> 16:29.360
Yeah, I finally understand why
people save money every year to travel.

16:29.360 --> 16:34.959
It's like by being in a different place,
it'll be like in a dream.

16:43.089 --> 16:46.204
(Library)

17:03.740 --> 17:06.839
Sheng, can you help me check my paper?

17:07.579 --> 17:08.879
What's wrong?

17:09.899 --> 17:14.544
The tutor said my writing is too vague.
Please help me revise it.

17:14.568 --> 17:16.232
If this version doesn't pass again,

17:16.232 --> 17:20.439
- I may be doomed.
- Let me take a look.

17:26.339 --> 17:30.200
The theoretical analysis here
is too excessive.

17:33.220 --> 17:37.160
For this section,
you should check some recent hot news

17:37.160 --> 17:40.520
to substantiate your theory
with corresponding examples.

17:41.500 --> 17:45.459
- As expected of you, Sheng. Carry on.
- Why don't you send it to me?

17:45.459 --> 17:48.936
I'll carefully review it tonight.
I can't find all the problems like this.

17:48.936 --> 17:52.599
- Okay. I'll look for some news first.
- Okay.

18:01.642 --> 18:02.060
(Linglong)

18:02.060 --> 18:05.770
(The performance that day
was successful, congrats.)

18:05.770 --> 18:10.620
(Last time, you said
you would consider it.)

18:10.920 --> 18:12.840
(I still hope you can agree.
I am a qualified singer.)

18:12.840 --> 18:14.970
(You're a promising composer.)

18:14.970 --> 18:17.692
(I believe you won't be
disappointed collaborating with me.)

18:17.832 --> 18:21.900
(Also, your voice is great.
If possible, )

18:21.900 --> 18:28.599
(I hope we can collaborate,
not as harmonies but as a duet.)

18:36.379 --> 18:37.439
Sheng.

18:39.300 --> 18:40.359
Sheng.

18:41.939 --> 18:43.040
Sheng.

18:43.740 --> 18:46.399
What's wrong? You look so serious.

18:51.220 --> 18:54.480
Linglong invited me to compose music.

18:55.220 --> 18:59.000
Who? The rumored girlfriend of your man?

19:01.379 --> 19:03.919
A love rival came for you?

19:04.659 --> 19:06.040
What did she say?

19:10.859 --> 19:13.544
She invited me to compose music.

19:13.544 --> 19:17.839
She said she watched my live stream
and invited me for a duet.

19:18.740 --> 19:20.079
Duet?

19:26.020 --> 19:30.088
What's with that expression?
I told you because I want your advice.

19:30.088 --> 19:35.579
This is for you to decide.
If you two cooperate,

19:35.579 --> 19:38.240
I can imagine
what the netizens would say.

19:40.060 --> 19:45.960
I'm also worried about that.
But from a professional perspective,

19:45.960 --> 19:48.680
I think the opportunity
to cooperate with her is rare.

19:48.680 --> 19:54.760
Indeed, she retired from the circle
as she was too busy with work years ago.

19:55.460 --> 19:58.376
A talented singer with many supporters.

19:58.376 --> 20:00.919
Many wanted to work with her
but had no chance.

20:13.300 --> 20:17.270
(How about this? I'll give it a try.
If we find it doesn't work, )

20:17.270 --> 20:19.900
(we can terminate the contract
at any time.)

20:19.900 --> 20:22.344
(I'll offer a song first
without pre-payment.)

20:22.344 --> 20:26.040
(Let's see if it's what you want.
We can discuss the rest later.)

20:27.936 --> 20:29.756
(Incoming call from Mo Qingcheng)

20:29.939 --> 20:32.440
Linglong? You gave her your number?

20:32.440 --> 20:36.280
No, Qiang Qingci and I
are having lunch together at noon.

20:36.280 --> 20:39.220
Collect the books for me. I'm leaving.

20:39.220 --> 20:40.599
- No problem.
- Goodbye.

20:43.139 --> 20:47.460
We should meet at twelve o'clock, right?
I'm still in the library.

20:47.460 --> 20:51.240
Gu Sheng, this is Mo Bai speaking.

20:53.220 --> 20:54.399
Hello.

20:55.260 --> 21:02.800
Finally, I got to talk to you!
I've been begging Mr. Mo. I may cry.

21:04.060 --> 21:07.580
We are currently filming
next to your school.

21:07.580 --> 21:10.940
A girl broke her promise,
and hasn't showed up yet.

21:10.940 --> 21:16.800
I am in a hurry to take pictures,
so can you take over for her?

21:17.780 --> 21:20.519
- You want me to do a cosplay?
- Yes!

21:20.519 --> 21:25.119
We will handle costume and makeup.
You don't have to worry about anything.

21:25.119 --> 21:27.740
But I don't have any experience.
I'm afraid that I may fail you.

21:27.740 --> 21:33.160
You just need to stand here.
You've got me and Mu, so rest assured.

21:33.160 --> 21:36.479
- Mr. Mo will send you the location.
- Okay, I'll come over right away.

21:36.479 --> 21:37.879
Goodbye.

22:35.700 --> 22:39.420
- Sheng is here.
- Here to help. Very kind of her.

22:39.420 --> 22:43.480
- Take a sip of milk tea first.
- When did you arrive?

22:44.060 --> 22:46.910
I happen to have a seminar around here.

22:46.910 --> 22:49.759
I was going to meet you at school
early for lunch before that.

22:49.759 --> 22:52.240
I didn't expect a phone call from Mo Bai
would summon you over.

22:52.264 --> 22:56.144
What? I begged you for a long time!
Sheng is so kind!

22:56.168 --> 22:59.100
She is always there when you need her.

22:59.176 --> 23:01.079
You've got a good girlfriend.

23:03.099 --> 23:06.080
- Shall we put on makeup first?
- Okay.

23:06.080 --> 23:13.560
That's our makeup artist, Wang. Come.
This is Wang. And this is Gu.

23:13.560 --> 23:14.900
- Hello.
- Hello.

23:14.900 --> 23:16.816
You should take care of her makeup.

23:16.840 --> 23:20.744
We don't have a dedicated make-up room.
So please bear with it.

23:20.744 --> 23:22.700
- Please.
- It's okay.

23:22.700 --> 23:24.960
- Okay.
- Then let's go do the makeup first.

23:24.960 --> 23:26.720
- Okay.
- Go ahead.

23:26.720 --> 23:28.359
I'll be going then.

23:33.859 --> 23:36.280
You're a model boyfriend,
always by her side.

23:42.859 --> 23:45.280
Your skin is really nice,
just like Mu's.

23:46.500 --> 23:49.680
Not as good as his.
He doesn't even have pores on his face.

23:49.680 --> 23:52.630
I wonder how he has such good skin.

23:52.630 --> 23:56.399
He doesn't seem to be a skin-care type.

23:58.780 --> 24:00.119
You've followed me all the way here.

24:00.119 --> 24:03.940
You said you would quit
and you wouldn't hang out with Yu!

24:03.940 --> 24:05.960
Are we that familiar?

24:07.460 --> 24:11.460
- You scum!
- Don't move. The mascara isn't dry yet.

24:11.460 --> 24:13.100
- I am a scum.
- Okay.

24:13.100 --> 24:18.780
That guy turned into a womaniser
soon after he had some fame, so lame.

24:18.780 --> 24:21.239
I'm telling you,
we had a normal breakup.

24:21.239 --> 24:24.760
- Scum.
- Scum.

24:26.579 --> 24:27.919
They've come to blows.

24:44.300 --> 24:48.720
- Are you okay? Did you get hurt?
- Who are you?

24:52.020 --> 24:53.760
Hitting a little girl,

24:55.300 --> 24:58.480
- do you even consider yourself a man?
- What's it to you?

25:04.419 --> 25:11.400
Mu. So you two are in the same group?
Mu, you're something, aren't you?

25:11.400 --> 25:15.680
Being senior and famous,
so you can bully people as you wish?

25:15.680 --> 25:20.359
Are you blind? I did not hit you.
Call out to him if you dare!

25:21.220 --> 25:24.720
- A man has hit a girl?
- I'll only curse at you.

25:24.720 --> 25:31.580
What? Three of you beating me alone?
You're really something.

25:31.580 --> 25:34.660
I bullied you, so what?

25:34.660 --> 25:40.744
Don't come near me!
Don't you dare to touch me once!

25:40.744 --> 25:44.440
If you lay a hand on me today,
I will post this online tomorrow.

25:44.440 --> 25:50.320
Post the deed of our righteous rescue?
Or we bullied others with our power?

25:52.139 --> 25:57.979
Geez. You really should consider
why you're being beaten today.

25:57.979 --> 26:01.560
And I'll stay here with you
until you figure it out, alright?

26:07.099 --> 26:08.560
Wait for me.

26:16.859 --> 26:19.899
- Sorry, it was an emergency.
- Thank you.

26:19.899 --> 26:24.279
Alright. Hurry back and start filming.
I'll treat everyone once we finish.

26:24.279 --> 26:26.140
- Let's go.
- Go ahead.

26:26.140 --> 26:29.000
Let's call a cab for her.
You go home first.

26:30.099 --> 26:32.369
- I will take you down.
- We should go together.

26:32.369 --> 26:34.859
They can start filming first.
We can still make it after this.

26:34.859 --> 26:37.399
- Okay.
- Let's go.

26:37.939 --> 26:39.679
- Go.
- I'll accompany them.

26:45.939 --> 26:49.560
I suddenly have a good feeling
for the words "bullying by power".

26:52.339 --> 26:53.339
Let's go.

26:56.419 --> 27:03.280
That lady, lean your body to that side.
Okay. Three, two, one, get ready.

27:06.540 --> 27:07.899
- Okay.
- Wait a moment.

27:07.899 --> 27:09.480
Okay.

27:10.460 --> 27:15.119
How about we have some interaction?
For example, you can put your hand here.

27:15.119 --> 27:20.000
- Here?
- Right. Try act cute. Face the camera.

27:20.000 --> 27:21.619
- Okay.
- Let's continue.

27:21.619 --> 27:29.000
Good. Three, two, one, hold on.

27:30.419 --> 27:34.299
- Wait a minute. We can interact.
- We can change positions.

27:34.299 --> 27:37.700
- Everyone can adjust the poses.
- Just smile gently like this.

27:37.700 --> 27:39.619
- Around the mouth?
- Right, just a slight smile.

27:39.619 --> 27:41.240
- Like this?
- Right.

27:42.339 --> 27:46.119
Ready? Three, two, one.

27:47.500 --> 27:48.960
The last one now.

27:53.099 --> 27:55.200
Alright everyone, let's wrap it up.

27:56.279 --> 27:58.040
- Everyone has worked hard.
- Thank you for your hard word.

27:58.040 --> 28:01.600
- Leave the props there and get changed.
- Fine.

28:01.600 --> 28:03.280
- Let's go.
- Don't leave anything behind.

28:03.280 --> 28:07.931
Thank you for your help today.
It's perfect. Really.

28:07.955 --> 28:08.859
We'll get our clothes changed now.

28:08.859 --> 28:09.720
- Okay.
- Let's go.

28:09.720 --> 28:12.159
Your boyfriend is really handsome.

28:15.020 --> 28:20.439
- Thank you.
- He would be a top star if he joins us.

28:20.980 --> 28:24.560
No, he doesn't like
to be in the limelight.

28:27.139 --> 28:28.359
What a pity!

28:29.659 --> 28:32.700
Follow me after putting down the props.
Makeup removers are in the make-up room.

28:32.700 --> 28:35.679
- I also have makeup remover.
- Okay.

28:37.740 --> 28:41.590
Make-up room will definitely be crowded.
I should not occupy one.

28:41.590 --> 28:44.019
I'll just go to the restroom downstairs.

28:44.019 --> 28:48.380
Fine, I have a sample of remover here.
Will it be enough?

28:48.380 --> 28:50.240
- It's enough. Thank you.
- Then I'll go first.

28:50.240 --> 28:51.960
- Okay.
- Thank you.

28:53.300 --> 28:55.520
- Let's take the stairs down from here.
- Okay.

28:58.939 --> 29:02.980
- How do you think of my performance?
- I think you were in a great state.

29:02.980 --> 29:04.919
And Mu and the others
have been teaching you.

29:10.099 --> 29:14.619
- Are you sure there are fewer people?
- Then we should go back upstairs.

29:14.619 --> 29:15.879
Okay.

29:19.500 --> 29:22.040
There are no more places
to get changed on other floors?

29:22.040 --> 29:26.920
There should be some with many people
and I'm dressed like this.

29:26.920 --> 29:29.575
At least we are dressed
the same up there.

29:29.599 --> 29:35.320
- Let's wait for them finishing changing.
- Okay.

29:45.179 --> 29:46.480
It's quite pretty.

29:48.260 --> 29:51.800
I mean, you look really good like this.

29:55.020 --> 29:59.408
You were so handsome just now.
My heart beat so fast.

29:59.432 --> 30:00.540
Really?

30:00.540 --> 30:05.320
That guy really deserved to be hit.
He was really annoying and infuriating.

30:07.139 --> 30:13.459
I originally thought
you were quite elegant.

30:13.459 --> 30:16.439
I didn't expect
that you would also hit someone.

30:18.339 --> 30:22.480
We can't just stand by
and watch that girl get hit, right?

30:23.659 --> 30:27.639
I saw you getting hit
for others last time.

30:28.260 --> 30:30.000
That time at the hospital entrance?

30:33.260 --> 30:40.320
- Does that kind of thing happen often?
- It just so happened that time.

30:41.859 --> 30:43.280
That's good.

30:53.500 --> 30:55.159
Are you

30:56.220 --> 30:57.760
worried about me?

31:10.980 --> 31:13.639
Aren't you afraid

31:14.460 --> 31:20.520
that I like your voice more
than I like you as a person?

31:23.659 --> 31:25.679
Whatever part of me you like,

31:26.339 --> 31:28.320
it's still me, right?

31:29.220 --> 31:31.368
There is nothing wrong with that.

31:31.368 --> 31:36.839
At least, I have something
attractive to you.

33:04.579 --> 33:10.320
The lipstick is too thick,
and it's not good for your health.

33:11.659 --> 33:13.240
But I'm okay with it.

33:17.379 --> 33:18.439
Let's go upstairs.

33:39.300 --> 33:41.760
This new bag I bought looks nice, right?

33:47.700 --> 33:48.800
What's wrong?

34:17.660 --> 34:18.959
It's clean?

34:39.220 --> 34:45.080
Gu, you haven't removed makeup yet?
Did you eat something with lipstick on?

34:50.220 --> 34:54.200
- It came off?
- It is not good for your health.

34:56.019 --> 34:59.439
But it's okay. The brands I used
are all plant-based.

34:59.439 --> 35:02.620
- Next time you should pay attention.
- Okay.

35:02.620 --> 35:07.880
Men's view of lipstick is limited.
Last time, I put on a colored lip balm.

35:07.880 --> 35:11.368
My husband was too scared to kiss me
until I told him it's okay.

35:11.368 --> 35:14.976
It's just lip balm and it's mango-flavored.

35:15.000 --> 35:20.979
- So we should use couple's lipstick.
- You always have great ideas.

35:20.979 --> 35:22.720
Gu Sheng is back.

35:23.939 --> 35:27.919
Did you not remove your makeup,
or just the lipstick?

35:30.580 --> 35:38.359
The restroom downstairs was crowded,
so I got pushed out after a while.

35:39.059 --> 35:41.680
Aren't you supposed to have a seminar?
What time is it?

35:42.379 --> 35:45.200
- It's about time.
- So, you're not eating then?

35:45.224 --> 35:48.624
I was going to,
but I'm here helping you out.

35:48.648 --> 35:50.100
Everyone's hungry now.

35:50.100 --> 35:55.740
My bad. How about you go to the seminar
and Sheng joins us for a meal.

35:55.740 --> 35:59.080
In the evening,
let's go to karaoke together afterwards.

35:59.660 --> 36:02.879
You come over after the seminar?
Is that a good idea?

36:03.740 --> 36:05.839
What do you want me to say?

36:07.979 --> 36:11.970
Do you have no time
or have to work overtime tonight?

36:12.052 --> 36:14.000
I don't have to work overtime.

36:14.000 --> 36:19.020
They're having one-on-one date today,
and you turned it into a party now.

36:19.020 --> 36:22.039
Oh, look at me. I'm an idiot.

36:24.220 --> 36:26.039
You've got to go?

36:27.620 --> 36:32.519
- Then, will you go to the karaoke?
- Sure he will.

36:34.620 --> 36:38.820
- If you go, I will be there.
- When does it end?

36:38.820 --> 36:41.730
It will finish before it gets dark.

36:41.730 --> 36:45.280
You know Mu and Mo Bai well.
Just feel free.

36:45.280 --> 36:52.359
- Order whatever you want later.
- Haven't you found yourself annoying?

36:53.820 --> 36:57.999
Didn't you say that everyone loves me?

36:59.339 --> 37:02.120
- Then I'll wait for you.
- Okay.

37:03.339 --> 37:06.560
- Then I'll leave Gu Sheng in your care.
- Okay.

37:06.560 --> 37:08.300
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

37:08.300 --> 37:09.640
- I'm leaving.
- Goodbye.

37:09.640 --> 37:10.680
Goodbye.

37:12.859 --> 37:14.679
Gu, let's get changed.

37:14.679 --> 37:16.600
- Okay.
- Let's go down and look for them.

37:16.600 --> 37:17.620
- Go.
- Go.

37:17.620 --> 37:22.680
- Everyone loves you?
- Hard to resist me! Got a problem?

37:25.660 --> 37:27.979
- Anyone over there wants milk tea?
- Here.

37:27.979 --> 37:29.059
- Come on.
- Here.

37:29.059 --> 37:33.160
- Yes.
- Who drinks milk tea in a karaoke?

37:33.160 --> 37:34.959
Do you think everyone is like you?

37:35.580 --> 37:38.560
- Let's toast to your hard work.
- Thank you.

37:38.560 --> 37:42.560
- Gu, you really resemble someone.
- Thank you.

37:42.560 --> 37:43.959
- Really.
- Who is it?

37:43.959 --> 37:47.780
- The 10th anniversary of Perfect Voice.
- That one!

37:47.780 --> 37:51.020
- The one in ancient costume.
- The girl who sang harmony for Wang Ke.

37:51.020 --> 37:53.059
- Shengshengman.
- Yes, Shengshengman.

37:53.059 --> 37:58.739
- I thought I've seen you somewhere.
- Right, it really does.

37:58.739 --> 38:01.920
- So alike.
- It may be because of the long hair.

38:01.920 --> 38:03.399
- No, it's not.
- Really?

38:03.399 --> 38:08.560
What are you two talking about?
Go choose some songs. Hurry!

38:08.560 --> 38:11.359
- I have a song to choose.
- Come on.

38:11.563 --> 38:13.576
♪ The lotus grow very well ♪

38:13.576 --> 38:15.716
♪ Pour the wine, read an ancient poem ♪

38:15.740 --> 38:17.680
- Mr. Mo, why are you so late?
- I just finished the meeting.

38:17.680 --> 38:19.680
Quick, take a seat.

38:22.660 --> 38:25.580
- You've been here for a while?
- Mr. Mo, what would you like to drink?

38:25.580 --> 38:26.640
Here.

38:28.180 --> 38:31.600
You were so handsome back then,
I'm telling you.

38:33.180 --> 38:35.856
- I've chosen a lot of songs.
- What have you chosen?

38:35.880 --> 38:39.504
"Bones to Sand",
Qiang Qingci's signature song.

38:39.528 --> 38:42.640
I remember it was the first song
he performed publicly.

38:42.640 --> 38:45.510
He sang it in the live room
with Shengshengman there.

38:45.510 --> 38:49.240
Shengshengman?
Isn't that a song for men?

38:50.100 --> 38:52.539
- Yes.
- But they surely won't sing it well.

38:52.539 --> 38:55.900
- Do you want me to sing?
- Ask the young lady's boyfriend.

38:55.900 --> 39:00.560
- You're likely to be discovered.
- How embarrassing.

39:00.560 --> 39:02.700
- Are you?
- Exactly.

39:02.700 --> 39:09.959
- Come on, hurry up.
- Can you sing "Bones to Sand"?

39:11.499 --> 39:14.820
- Yes.
- Can you sing that for us?

39:14.820 --> 39:16.879
- Please!
- I...

39:16.879 --> 39:20.680
Yes!

39:29.859 --> 39:32.066
♪ I traveled all over the world ♪

39:32.066 --> 39:34.659
♪ I trod through the ocean
of flowers and mountains ♪

39:34.659 --> 39:36.820
(He changed his vocal range to sing.)

39:36.820 --> 39:38.818
♪ Looking back,
the best years have gone by ♪

39:38.818 --> 39:43.540
♪ Who can bear to hear
the dreary sound of a Qiang flute ♪

39:43.540 --> 39:45.800
It's completely different
from Qiang Qingci.

39:46.140 --> 39:50.240
- Yes.
- Qiang's still got something.

39:51.320 --> 39:52.990
♪ I laugh, knowing even
my glorious achievements ♪

39:52.990 --> 39:54.260
♪ Cannot withstand the burial of time ♪

39:54.260 --> 39:56.080
- So good.
- Deep and unassuming.

39:56.080 --> 39:58.120
He's got his own style.

40:00.459 --> 40:02.319
♪ Clouds and moon accompany me ♪

40:02.319 --> 40:04.180
♪ I ride a horse back into the desert ♪

40:04.180 --> 40:05.960
♪ A long spear pokes through ♪

40:05.960 --> 40:07.999
♪ What does fate matter ♪

40:07.999 --> 40:10.399
♪ If love and hatred can't be avoided ♪

40:10.399 --> 40:14.400
♪ Under the flying sand lie the bones ♪

40:14.400 --> 40:16.939
♪ I am destined
to be a bloodthirsty warrior ♪

40:16.939 --> 40:19.180
♪ Only one survives in victory ♪

40:19.180 --> 40:22.060
♪ Raise my eyebrows
and sweep away all doubts ♪

40:22.060 --> 40:23.019
♪ It's worth ♪

40:23.019 --> 40:24.949
♪ My youth's love for hardships ♪

40:24.949 --> 40:26.640
♪ I am invincible and lonely ♪

40:26.640 --> 40:29.860
♪ Who can outshine me ♪

40:29.860 --> 40:33.640
♪ Ancient landscapes feel like
it was just yesterday ♪

40:33.640 --> 40:37.600
♪ Who has passed by in this dream ♪

40:37.600 --> 40:39.580
♪ This tarnished iron armor ♪

40:39.580 --> 40:44.560
♪ Has been hidden in legends ♪

40:44.560 --> 40:47.220
- Excellent!
- Thank you.

40:47.220 --> 40:48.580
- Oh, my! It's so good!
- I will just sing this part.

40:48.580 --> 40:53.220
- Sure. Though it's not like Qiang Qingci.
- You are really amazing.

40:53.220 --> 40:59.439
- Exactly, this is just too good.
- How did you change your voice like that?

40:59.979 --> 41:03.519
This is a basic quality
of a professional dubbing actor.

41:04.459 --> 41:07.339
- What are you doing? Go choose a song.
- Okay, let's go.

41:07.339 --> 41:08.700
- Same for you.
- Let's go. Quick.

41:08.700 --> 41:10.300
- Would you like to take a walk?
- I'm too embarrassed to sing.

41:10.300 --> 41:12.320
Come, let's have a drink.

41:15.180 --> 41:19.680
- Why leave as soon as you arrived?
- Don't meddle in the matters of couples.

41:22.100 --> 41:23.479
It's sweet, isn't it?

41:25.220 --> 41:29.260
- Where are we going?
- Are you familiar with this area?

41:29.260 --> 41:33.439
- No.
- Then we will just stroll around.

41:50.979 --> 41:52.240
Blueberry flavor?

41:52.780 --> 41:53.959
Would you like some?

41:55.700 --> 42:01.200
- You always eat this before dubbing.
- I should take good care of it.

42:05.979 --> 42:11.280
Let's go that way. There are more lights
and there should be more stores.

42:14.140 --> 42:15.439
Sorry.

42:20.939 --> 42:22.200
Be careful.

42:29.180 --> 42:35.439
Do you know any nearby bus stops
to my campus?

42:36.300 --> 42:41.039
- Or maybe the subway. Later...
- I do.

42:42.637 --> 42:48.589
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

42:48.735 --> 42:51.998
♪ My heart is racing ♪

42:52.584 --> 42:56.775
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

42:56.799 --> 43:01.532
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

43:02.399 --> 43:05.472
♪ What kind of look ♪

43:06.484 --> 43:10.408
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

43:10.408 --> 43:13.636
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

43:13.636 --> 43:17.171
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

43:17.171 --> 43:22.472
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

43:22.472 --> 43:24.279
♪ I love you ♪

43:24.279 --> 43:27.521
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

43:27.521 --> 43:30.829
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

43:30.829 --> 43:36.232
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

43:36.232 --> 43:40.189
♪ I love you ♪

43:51.583 --> 43:56.792
♪ Hey, I have decided ♪

43:57.521 --> 44:00.400
♪ In every starry sky ♪

44:01.535 --> 44:05.128
♪ I want to get closer to you ♪

44:05.128 --> 44:10.463
♪ Hey, I want to hug you ♪

44:11.141 --> 44:13.994
♪ I've never been so sure ♪

44:15.159 --> 44:18.472
♪ I miss you so much ♪

44:18.472 --> 44:22.362
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

44:22.362 --> 44:25.849
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

44:25.855 --> 44:31.035
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

44:31.035 --> 44:32.816
♪ I love you ♪

44:32.816 --> 44:36.083
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

44:36.086 --> 44:39.335
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

44:39.335 --> 44:45.048
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

44:45.072 --> 44:48.563
♪ I love you ♪

44:56.831 --> 44:58.644
♪ I am with you ♪

44:58.644 --> 45:00.326
♪ I love you ♪

45:00.326 --> 45:03.438
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

45:03.438 --> 45:06.768
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

45:06.768 --> 45:12.197
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

45:12.221 --> 45:13.936
♪ I love you ♪

45:13.936 --> 45:16.963
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

45:16.963 --> 45:20.480
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

45:20.480 --> 45:26.009
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

45:26.009 --> 45:29.890
♪ I love you ♪
